        <!-- story header -->
        <div class="postheader">
          <div class="postinfo">
            <p>Posted by <a href="http://antonymarcano.com/blog/author/antonymarcano/" title="Posts by AntonyMarcano ">AntonyMarcano</a> in <a href="http://antonymarcano.com/blog/category/agile-2/" title="View all posts in Agile" rel="category tag">Agile</a>, <a href="http://antonymarcano.com/blog/category/bddatdd/" title="View all posts in BDD/ATDD" rel="category tag">BDD/ATDD</a>, <a href="http://antonymarcano.com/blog/category/business-analysis/" title="View all posts in Business Analysis" rel="category tag">Business Analysis</a>, <a href="http://antonymarcano.com/blog/category/software-development-2/" title="View all posts in Software Development" rel="category tag">Software Development</a>, <a href="http://antonymarcano.com/blog/category/software-testing-2/" title="View all posts in Software Testing" rel="category tag">Software Testing</a>, <a href="http://antonymarcano.com/blog/category/uncategorized/" title="View all posts in Uncategorized" rel="category tag">Uncategorized</a> on October 2, 2011 </p>
